		<title>生病貓終生必須吃藥！暖心飼主用「小巧思」讓牠不再抗拒 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/13/%e7%94%9f%e7%97%85%e8%b2%93%e7%b5%82%e7%94%9f%e5%bf%85%e9%a0%88%e5%90%83%e8%97%a5%ef%bc%81%e6%9a%96%e5%bf%83%e9%a3%bc%e4%b8%bb%e7%94%a8%e3%80%8c%e5%b0%8f%e5%b7%a7%e6%80%9d%e3%80%8d%e8%ae%93%e7%89%a0/</link>
		
