		<title>狗狗毛裡藏危機！小心隱藏的「寄生蟲」恐害牠出現嚴重皮膚病</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/13/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e6%af%9b%e8%a3%a1%e8%97%8f%e5%8d%b1%e6%a9%9f%ef%bc%81%e5%b0%8f%e5%bf%83%e9%9a%b1%e8%97%8f%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e5%af%84%e7%94%9f%e8%9f%b2%e3%80%8d%e6%81%90%e5%ae%b3%e7%89%a0%e5%87%ba/</link>
		
